com.bigdata.rdf.internal.impl.extensions

Class DerivedNumericsExtension<V extends BigdataValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.internal.impl.extensions.DerivedNumericsExtension<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExtension<V>

    public class DerivedNumericsExtension<V extends BigdataValue>
extends Object
implements IExtension<V>
    This implementation of IExtension implements inlining for literals that represent the derived numeric types:
    • xsd:nonPositiveInteger
    • xsd:negativeInteger
    • xsd:nonNegativeInteger
    • xsd:positiveInteger
